Excel Spreadsheets for Chrome

This Chrome extension allows users to adjust the brightness and background color of the Microsoft Cloud page. With a simple slider and color picker, users can customize their viewing experience to reduce eye strain and enhance readability. Ideal for anyone working on cloud-based spreadsheets or data management tasks.
